    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The FEA model ensemble demonstrates adequate credibility for the COU. All three QoIs satisfy the pre-specified E/uval < 1.96 and <10% difference acceptance criteria. Twelve of thirteen V&V 40 credibility factors meet or exceed required levels; the single shortfall (Test conditions, achieved level 1 vs. required level 2) is accepted given the standardized ASTM F1717 protocol and regulatory precedent. Overall credibility is sufficient for a Medium model risk level, Medium model influence, Medium decision consequence context. The assessment team accepts the package and recommends submission to FDA.",
